  "text": "Following this relational approach, we construct the parametric relational lifting of Giry monad to describe differential privacy for continuous random samplings. This lifting forms a graded monad on the category BRel(Meas) in the sense of [CITATION_1] . The axioms of graded monad correspond to the (sequential) composition law of differential privacy.",
